description:
#HappyNewYearFamily #JehovahShalomAcapella  #AfricanAcapella #Gospelmusic

Give everything to God and
He will give you everything, too!
May this New Year give you
more hope and reasons to live happily!

Get our music : 
Apple music : https://apple.co/32KGeme
Spotify Music : https://spoti.fi/3EGcvZ2

Lyrics;
Mama, nawe Taata, we want to wish you a happy new year year year year,
Sister, nawe  Brother, we want to wish you a happy new year year year year,
Cousin, nawe Nephew, we want to wish you a happy new year year year year,
Every one, everybody, we want to wish you a happy new year year year,

Chorus
(We wish you, we wish you, we wish you...
we want to wish you a happy new year year year...)x2

We thank God, for our life, we are very well happy new year,
Everything is going to be good in Jesus name, happy new year,
We pray to God to overcome, we pray to God for a better life,
let me tell you never lose hope, never lose faith happy new year...

Chorus
(We wish you, we wish you, we wish you...
we want to wish you a happy new year year year...)x2
